				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><table class="infobox vcard" cellspacing="3" style="border-spacing: 3px; width:22em;">
<tr>
<th colspan="2" class="fn" style="text-align:center; font-size:125%; font-weight:bold; background-color: #bfe0bf">Irving Berlin</th>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:BerlinPortrait1.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/da/BerlinPortrait1.jpg/220px-BerlinPortrait1.jpg" width="220" height="289" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/da/BerlinPortrait1.jpg/330px-BerlinPortrait1.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/da/BerlinPortrait1.jpg 2x" /></a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; background-color: #bfe0bf">Background information</th>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;">Birth name</th>
<td class="nickname" style="">Israel Isidore Baline (Beilin)</td>
</tr>
<tr class="">
